  <brief_title>Can Changes of Rest Energy Expenditure Indicate the Outcome in Critical Patients?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Change of Rest Energy Expenditure in Early Intensive Care Unit Stay is a Reliable Predictor of Outcome in Critical Ill Patient</official_title>
  <sponsors>
